column2: SELECT G.u_err, G.g_err, G.r_err, G.i_err, G.z_err, a.h_alpha_flux_err, emline.sigmaStars as emline_vdisp FROM Galaxy as G join GalSpecLine as a on G.SpecobjID = a.SpecObjID join stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS pca ON G.specobjid = pca.specobjid join emissionLinesPort as emline on pca.specobjid = emline.specobjid JOIN specObj as sp ON emline.specobjid = sp.specobjid JOIN mangaDAPall as mn on G.htmID = mn.htmID
